PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FAn international effort is underway to
OL,7,Fcontain an Ebola outbreak in the
OL,8,FDemocratic Republic of Congo (DRC) and
OL,9,FUganda ` with the United States
OL,10,Flooking to relocate a "small number"
OL,11,Fof citizens exposed to the virus.
OL,13,FOn Sunday, the World Health
OL,14,FOrganisation (WHO) declared the
OL,15,Fepidemic a "public health emergency of
OL,16,Finternational concern".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FIt is yet to meet the more serious
OL,7,Fcriteria of a "pandemic emergency",
OL,8,Fbut nonetheless WHO warned the
OL,9,Fincreasing number of cases and deaths
OL,10,Fpoints towards "a potentially much
OL,11,Flarger outbreak than what is currently
OL,12,Fbeing detected and reported".
OL,14,FSo far there have been ten confirmed
OL,15,Fcases and 336 suspected cases,
OL,16,Fincluding 88 deaths in the DRC, the US
OL,17,FCentres for Disease Control and
OL,18,FPrevention (CDC) said on Sunday.
OL,26,@rD@POUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FThe public health agency added that it
OL,7,Fwas supporting partners in efforts to
OL,8,Frelocate "a small number of Americans
OL,9,Fwho are directly affected" by the
OL,10,Foutbreak.
OL,12,FSeveral Americans in the DRC were
OL,13,Fbelieved to have been exposed to the
OL,14,Fvirus, including some deemed high
OL,15,Frisk, health news outlet STAT reported
OL,16,Fon Sunday.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FITV News' North American partner CNN
OL,7,Fcould not independently verify the
OL,8,Freports and has reached out to the CDC
OL,9,Fand the US Department of State for
OL,10,Fcomment.
OL,12,FDr Satish Pillai, the CDC's Ebola
OL,13,FResponse Incident Manager, declined on
OL,14,FSunday to say whether any Americans
OL,15,Fwere among those who had been infected.
OL,17,FAt a press briefing, he said the CDC
OL,18,Fwas "actively assessing the situation
OL,19,Fon the ground and we aren't going to
OL,20,Fcomment on individual disposition".
OL,26,@zD@EOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FThe CDC said it was deploying
OL,7,Fresources already in the country to
OL,8,Fhelp with efforts including
OL,9,Fsurveillance, contact tracing and
OL,10,Flaboratory testing, and will mobilise
OL,11,Fadditional support from the agency's
OL,12,Fheadquarters in Atlanta.
OL,14,FDr Pillai said the CDC was unaware of
OL,15,Fany exposure on international flights
OL,16,Fand noted that both countries have
OL,17,Fexit screening measures in place to
OL,18,Fprevent the spread of the virus
OL,19,Fthrough travel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FInternational coordination is being
OL,7,Framped up to prevent the epidemic's
OL,8,Fspread as experts warn of "extremely
OL,9,Fconcerning" conditions.
OL,11,FThe DRC's health minister, Samuel
OL,12,FRoger Kamba, said Sunday that three
OL,13,Ftreatment centres were being opened in
OL,14,Fthe affected region to increase
OL,15,Fcapacity amid the outbreak.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FWHO said the outbreak is affecting the
OL,7,Fcountry's remote northeastern Ituri
OL,8,Fprovince. In neighbouring Uganda, two
OL,9,Flaboratory-confirmed cases, including
OL,10,Fone death, have so far been reported
OL,11,Fin the country's capital Kampala, WHO
OL,12,Freported.
OL,14,FThe latest outbreak is being driven by
OL,15,Fthe Bundibugyo strain, one of several
OL,16,Fviruses that can cause Ebola disease,
OL,17,FWHO said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FThe organisation has called the
OL,7,Foutbreak "extraordinary" as there are
OL,8,Fcurrently no approved treatments or
OL,9,Fvaccines specific to the Bundibugyo
OL,10,Fvirus.
OL,12,FEbola symptoms include fever, muscle
OL,13,Fpain, rash and sometimes bleeding. The
OL,14,Fvirus is transmitted through direct
OL,15,Fcontact with bodily fluids, including
OL,16,Fthe handling of contaminated materials
OL,17,For someone who has died from the
OL,18,Fdisease.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FThe fatality rate involving the
OL,7,FBundibugyo strain is estimated to be
OL,8,Fbetween 25% and 40%, according to
OL,9,FDoctors Without Borders, or Medecins
OL,10,FSans Frontieres (MSF).
OL,12,F"The number of cases and deaths we are
OL,13,Fseeing in such a short timeframe,
OL,14,Fcombined with the spread across
OL,15,Fseveral health zones and now across
OL,16,Fthe border, is extremely concerning,"
OL,17,FTrish Newport, MSF's emergency program
OL,18,Fmanager, said on Saturday.
OL,26,@qD@^rrrD@LqrtD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FAbout seven metric tons of emergency
OL,7,Fmedical supplies, including protective
OL,8,Fequipment, tents and beds, arrived in
OL,9,Fthe Ituri capital Bunia on Sunday to
OL,10,F"help scale up frontline response
OL,11,Fefforts".
OL,13,FComplicating response efforts is that
OL,14,Fthe outbreak is occurring on top of a
OL,15,Fhumanitarian crisis, where conflict in
OL,16,Fthe DRC's eastern provinces has
OL,17,Fdisplaced millions of people and
OL,18,Fweakened health systems.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
