OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn Uganda, the two confirmed cases in
OL,12,FKampala have no known connection to
OL,13,Feach other, which is "often a warning
OL,14,Fsign that the outbreak in the DRC is
OL,15,Flarger than health authorities can
OL,16,Fcurrently see," Adrian Esterman,
OL,17,Fprofessor and chair of Biostatistics
OL,18,Fat Adelaide University, said in a
OL,19,Fstatement.
OL,26,@uD@VOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FThe suspected deaths include four
OL,7,Fhealth workers, according to WHO.
OL,9,FDr Matt Mason, senior lecturer for the
OL,10,FSchool of Health at the University of
OL,11,Fthe Sunshine Coast said this "raises
OL,12,Fserious concerns about gaps in
OL,13,Finfection prevention and control and
OL,14,Fthe potential for amplification within
OL,15,Fhealth facilities, leading to the
OL,16,Fwider community".
OL,18,FThis is the 17th Ebola outbreak in the
OL,19,FDRC since the virus was first
OL,20,Fidentified in 1976, according to WHO.
OL,26,@sD@^OUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779174391
OL,3,CUS to relocate 'small number' of
OL,4,CAmericans exposed to Ebola outbreak
OL,6,FThe country is particularly prone to
OL,7,FEbola outbreaks in part because the
OL,8,Fvirus' "natural reservoir" is the
OL,9,Ffruit bat, which are found within the
OL,10,FDRC's forested areas, public health
OL,11,Fexpert Ahmed Ogwell, former deputy
OL,12,Fdirector-general at the Africa Centres
OL,13,Ffor Disease Control and Prevention,
OL,14,Ftold CNN.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@ZO]
